com.google.cloud.datastore

Class Key

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.datastore.BaseKey
      • com.google.cloud.datastore.IncompleteKey
        • com.google.cloud.datastore.Key
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class Key
extends IncompleteKey
    A key that is guaranteed to be complete and could be used to reference a Google Cloud Datastore Entity. This class is immutable.
    See Also:
    Google Cloud Datastore Entities, Properties, and Keys, Serialized Form
